tsn: gajaana ke nako ya go ala motheo wa kgolo e e tiileng fa re ya pele, kgolo e e tlhamang ditiro tse dingwe.

ssw: tinhlelo tesakhiwonchanti setfu sesikhatsi lesidze titasisita kutsi sikhule ngekunonopha.
tsn: lenaneo la rona la ditirelo la pakatelele le tla re thusa go gola ka lebelo.

ssw: tinhlelo tetfu tetemfundvo netemakhono titakwandzisa kukhicita kanye nekuncintsisana kwetfu.
tsn: mananeo a rona a thuto le bokgoni a tla oketsa kumo le bogaisani.

ssw: luhlelo lwetfu lwenchubomgomo lesebenta kutetimboni nekugcila kwetfu lokusha emisebentini lephelele, kutakwakha timboni leticinile naletemukela tisebenti letinyenti.
tsn: leanotiro la pholisi ya bodiredi mmogo le tebontshwa ya ditiro tse diswa, di tla aga madirelo a a maatla le a a ngokang badiri.

ssw: luhlelo lwetfu lwekutfutfukisa tindzawo tasemakhaya titakwenta ngcono umkhicito wasemakhaya, kanye netemphilo tebantfu labahlala etindzaweni tasemakhaya.
tsn: mananeo a rona a tlhabololo ya magae a tla tokafatsa kumo ya selegae mmogo le matshelo a batho ba ba tshelang mo mafelong a magae.

ssw: lokwesekela lisu letfu lekubuyisela umnotfo esimeni lesetayelekile nasekukhuliseni, luhlelo lwetfu lwekusisa ngetimali.
tsn: motheo wa mananeo a rona a tsosoloso le kgodiso ya ikonomi ke mananeo a peeletso ya madi.

ssw: kuleminyaka lemitsatfu letako, hulumende utawuchitsa imali lengemabhiliyoni emarandi langu-846 kusakhiwonchanti semmango.
tsn: mo dingwageng tse tharo tse di tlang, puso e tla dirisa r846 bilione malebana le dipopotheo tsa setshaba.

ssw: kutekutfutsa, sitawugcina siphindze senabise umsebenti wetfu wekuchumanisa tindzawo ngemigwaco.
tsn: mo go tsa dipalangwa, re tla tshola le go godisa mafaratlhatlha a ditsela.

ssw: sitawucinisekisa kutsi kuchumanisa kwetfu kwetindzawo ngaloliwe kuyetsembeka, futsi kuhlanganiswe kancono nemachweba etfu.
tsn: re tla netefatsa gore mafaratlhatlha a rona a diporo a a ikanyega, a kgona go gaisana, e bile a nyalana le go golagana botoka le boemelakepe.

ssw: kute kucinisekiswe kuniketwa kwemandla agezi, sisungule likomiti letindvuna lelibukene netemandla, kute kwentiwe luhlelo loluhlanganisile lweminyaka lengama-20.
tsn: go netefatsa kabo ya maatlamotlakase e e ikanyegang, re tlhomile komiti ya ditona ya maatlamotlakase, go re kgontsha go tlhama thulaganokgolagano ya dingwaga di le 20. gareng ga tse dingwe, thulagano e, e ya go leba botsayakarolo jwa batsweletsi ba maatlamotlakase ba ba ikemetseng ka bosi, mmogo le go sireletsa batlhoki kgatlhanong le tlhotlhwa ya motlakase e e tlhatlogang.

ssw: phakatsi kwaletinye tintfo, loku kutawubuka ekutibandzakanyeni kwebakhiciti bemandla labatimele, nasekuvikeleni labaphuyile ekwenyukeni kwemanani agezi.
tsn: re ya go tlhoma botsamaisi jo bo ikemetseng, jo bo sa golaganang le eskom holdings.

ssw: sitawusungula luhlelo lwekusebenta ngagezi lolutimele, lolwehlukile ku-eskom holdings.
tsn: eskom e tla tswelela go aga mothamo o o okeditsweng wa maatla, le go tokafatsa tlamelo ya diteisene tsa yona tsa maatlamotlakase.

ssw: eskom utawuchubeka nekwakha lamanye emandla ekukhicita emandla agezi aphindze ente ncono simo setiteshi takhe tagezi.
tsn: re tlhamile lekgotlakgakololo la matlafatso e e atolositsweng ya ikonomi ya go tlhomamisa thotloetso ya ikonomi e e akaretsang botlhe.

ssw: kucinisekisa kukhuliswa kwemnotfo lohlanganisako, kute sisite kukhula nentfutfuko, sisungule umkhandlu loweluleka ngeluhlelo lolwenabile lwekuniketa labamnyama emandla kutemnotfo, loluholwa ngumengameli.
tsn: tebo e e tshwanetseng go potlakelwa ya phetogo ya pholesi e tshwanetse go nna botsereganyi ka maikaelelo a go tlhola ditiro tsa baswa.

ssw: tiphakamiso titawubekwa kute kusitwe ngetimali etindlekweni tekucasha tisebenti talabasha, kute kukhutsatwe emafemu kutsi atsatse tisebenti letite lwati lwemsebenti lolwenele.
tsn: go ya go begwa ditshikhinyo tsa go etleetsa tlhotlhwa ya go thapa badiri ba baswa.

ssw: lokunye kwelulwa kwetinhlelo temisebenti yemmango nako kuyachutjwa.
tsn: se se tla rotloetsa madirelo go thapa badiri ba ba se nang maitemogelo.

ssw: loku kufaka ekhatsi sakhiwonchanti ezingeni lasekhaya nemiklamo lemikhulu kanye nemiklamo yekukwati kufundza nekubhala, kunakekela kwasemakhaya, kugcinwa kwetikolo kanye nemitamo yekukhulisa bantfwana labasebancane.
tsn: se se akaretsa madirelo a selegae, diporojeke tsa maano a boraro, diporojeke tsa puisokwalo, tlhokomelo ya fa gae, tlhokomelo ya dikolo le kgodiso kgolo ya bana go tswa kwa bonnyeng.

ssw: kulomnyaka lowengcile sisukumise sikhungo sekutfutfukisa lusha lwavelonkhe.
tsn: mo ngwageng o o fetileng re kgakotse mokgatlho wa bosetshaba wa tlhabololo ya baswa.

ssw: siyalele loluphiko kutsi lusungule imitimba yalo, eliveni lonkhe, kute lutewukwati kusita ekucondziseni tinhlelo tekutfutfukisa ngekhatsi kuhulumende.
tsn: re kaetse setheo se go potlakisa tlhamo ya makala a sona naga ka bophara gore se kgone go re thusa go tsenya mananeo a tlhabololo ya baswa o moseleng o o maleba mo pusong.

ssw: malunga lahloniphekile,ngalesikhatsi baphatsi bacala kuphatsa emnyakeni lowengcile, sitsembise kusebenta ngemandla kute sakhe umbuso lotfutfuke ngemandla.
tsn: maloko a a tlotlegang,fa botsamaiso joo bo tsena tirong ngogola, re itlamile go dira ka natla gore re age naga e e nonofileng ya tlhabololo.

ssw: sitsite kutakuba ngumbuso lophendvula etidzingweni nasetifisweni tebantfu, nalosebenta kancono nangekunonopha.
tsn: re rile naga e, e ya go tsibogela ditlhokwa le ditlhologelo tsa batho, mme e ya go nna naga e e dirang botoka, e ntse e direla ka lobelo lo lo okeditsweng.

ssw: lomnyaka, wa-2010, kutakuba ngumnyaka wekwenta.
tsn: ngwaga ono, 2010, e ya go nna ngwaga wa go dira.

ssw: luphawu loluchaza lokuphatsa kutakuba ngulolo lwekutsi kuyati lapho bantfu bahlala khona, kuvisisa tidzingo tabo futsi kuphendvula ngekunonopha.
tsn: ponagalo e e itlhaolang ya botsamaisi jono e ya go nna gore bo itse gore batho ba tshela kae, bo tlhaloganya ditlhokwa tsa batho mme bo tsibogela ditlhokwa tse, ka lobelo lo lo okeditsweng.

ssw: hulumende kumele asebente ngekunonopha, ngemandla nangekuhlakanipha.
tsn: puso e tshwanetse go dira ka lobelo lo lo okeditsweng, ka natla go gaisa mme e le ka manontlhotlho.

ssw: sitawulindzela sigungu lesiphetse kanye nemsebenti wahulumende kutsi bahambisane nalombono.
tsn: re lebeletse gore khuduthamaga le bodiredipuso bo inaakanye le maitlhomo a. re aga naga e e sokegetseng mo go direng le go diragatseng, mme re dira jaana ka go tokafatsa thulaganyo mmogo le kelotlhoko ya tiragatso le tlhatlhobo.

ssw: sakha umbuso logcile ekusebenteni, ngekwenta ncono kuhlela kanye netinhlelo tekulandzelela kusebenta nekulinganisa.
tsn: re tlhoka le go nyalanya maiteko a tekatekanyo ya bong le lenaneo la tiro la puso.

ssw: loluhlelo lwekwenta lutawucinisekisa kutsi bomake, bantfwana nebantfu labakhubatekile bakwati kufinyelela kumatfuba ekutitfutfukisa.
tsn: tiro e e tla netefatsa gore basadi, baswa le digole ba fitlhelela tshono ya tlhabololo.

ssw: sinentfokoto yekumemetela indlela lensha yekwenta tintfo kuhulumende.
tsn: re motlotlo go itsise tsela e ntshwa ya go dira dilo mo pusong.

ssw: umsebenti wematiko utawukalwa ngemiphumela, letfutfukiswe ngeluhlelo lwetfu lwekulandzelela kusebenta nekulinganisa.
tsn: tiro ya mafapha e tla lekanyetswa ka dipoelo tse di tlhamilweng go ya ka thulaganyo kelotlhoko ya tiragatso le tlhatlhobo.

ssw: tindvuna letibukene nemphumela lotsite, titawusayina namengameli sivumelwano lesichaza ngalokubanti ngekusebenta kwato.
tsn: ditona tse di rweleng maikarabelo a poelo e e rileng, di tla saena tumalano ya tiragatso e e tletseng, le moporesidente.

ssw: lesivumelwano sitawuchaza kutsi yini lokumele yentiwe, kanjani, ngubani, esikhatsini lesinganani nekutsi ngutiphi tindlela tekukala kanye netinsita letitawusetjentiswa.
tsn: tumalano e, e tla tlhalosa se se tshwanetseng go dirwa, gore se dirwa jang, ke mang, mo pakeng e e kae, go dirisiwa tekanyetso le didirisiwa dife.

ssw: njengobe nati, sitibophetele etintfweni letisihlanu letisetulu eluhlwini: imfundvo, temphilo, kutfutfukisa tindzawo tasemakhaya, kusungula imisebenti lemihle kanye nekulwa nebugebengu.
tsn: jaaka lo setse lo itse, re itlametse ditlapele tse tlhano:thuto, boitekanelo, tlhabololo ya metsemagae le bonno jwa batho, go tlhama ditiro tse di eletsegang, le go lwantsha bosenyi.

ssw: ngetulu kwaloko, sitawusebentela kwenta ncono kusebenta kahle kwahulumende wasemakhaya, kutfutfukiswa kwesakhiwonchanti kanye nekuhlaliswa kwebantfu.
tsn: go tlaleletsa fa, re tla dira ka natla go tokafatsa boleng jwa pusoselegae, tlhabololo ya dipopotheo lebonno jwa batho.

ssw: sitsembisa kwenta iminyakato leyinsika lelibangise ekutfolweni kwalemiphumela.
tsn: re ya go dira ditiro di le mmalwa go fitlhelela dipoelo tse.

ssw: sibeke imfundvo nekutfutfukiswa kwemakhono enkhabeni yetinchubomgomo talohulumende.
tsn: re beile thuto le tlhabololo ya bokgoni jaaka pinagare ya dipholesi tsa puso.

ssw: eluhlelweni lwetfu lwa-2010, sifuna kwenta ncono likhono lebantfwana betfu lekukwati kufundza, kubhala nekubala eminyakeni lesisekelo.
tsn: mo lenaneong la rona la 2010, re eletsa go tokafatsa bokgoni jwa bana ba rona jwa go buisa, go kwala le go bala mo dingwageng tsa kgato ya motheo.

ssw: ngaphandle kwekwenta loku, singete sakwati kwenta ncono lizinga lemfundvo.
tsn: fa re sa dire se, re ka se ka ra tokafatsa boleng jwa thuto.

ssw: tibalo temfundvo lesitibekele tona timalula kodvwa tinebungoti.
tsn: dintlhanaikaelelo tsa rona ka ga thuto di bonolo, le gale di botlhokwa.

ssw: sifuna bafundzi nemathishela babe sesikolweni, eklasini, ngesikhatsi, bafundza futsi bafundzisa ema-awa lasikhombisa ngelusuku.
tsn: re batla baithuti le barutabana ba nne kwa sekolong, mo phaposing, ka nako, ba ithuta le go ruta, diura di le supa ka letsatsi.

ssw: sitawusita bothishela ngekubanikela luhlelo lwetifundvo lwemalanga onkhe loluchaza kabanti.
tsn: re tla thusa barutabana ka go ba neela dithulaganyotiro tse di tletseng, tsa letsatsi le letsatsi.

ssw: kubafundzi, sitawuniketela ngetincwadzi temsebenti lokumalula kutisebentisa letibhalwe ngato tonkhe tilwimi letili-11.
tsn: go baithuti, re tla ba abela dibukatiro tse di ka dirisiwang bonolo, ka dipuo tsotlhe tse 11. go simolola monogwaga go ya pele, baithuti botlhe ba dikereite 3, 6 le 9 ba tla kwala diteko tsa puisokwalo le thutapalo tse di tla lekanyediwang ke balekanyetsi ba ba ikemetseng.

ssw: kusukela kulomnyaka kuya embili, onkhe emabanga lesi-3, 6 nele-9 batawubhala tivivinyo tekukwati kubhala nekubala kanye netenyumeresi lokutivivinyo letitawenganyelwa ngalokutimele.
tsn: re ikaelela go oketsa kelo ya phalolo ya diteko tse go tloga palogareng ya gajaana ya 35% le 40% go ya go bonnye, 60% ka 2014. dipholo di tla romelelwa batsadi gore ba sale morago tswelelopele ya bana.

ssw: ngetulu kwaloko, ngasinye setikolo tetfu letingu-27 000 sitawuhlolwa tikhulu telitiko lemfundvo lesisekelo.
tsn: go tlaleletsa fa, sekolo sengwe le sengwe sa tse 27 000 se tla tlhatlhojwa ke batlhankedi go tswa lefapheng la thuto ya motheo.

ssw: loku kutawurekhodwa embikweni lobhaliwe locwaningekako.
tsn: se se tla kwalwa mo rekotong ya pegelo e e kwadilweng e e ka runwang.

ssw: sihlose kwenyusa linani lebafundzi bamatikuletjeni labakhona kwemukelwa emanyuvesi kutsi lifinyelele ku-175 000 ngemnyaka nga-2014.
tsn: re ikaelela go oketsa palo ya baithuti ba materiki ba ba ka kgonang go amogelwa kwa diyunibesithing go ya go 175 000 ka ngwaga ka 2014. re rotloetsa batsadi go dirisana le rona go netefatsa katlego se.

ssw: semukela sitatimende semnyaka lowengcile lesakhishwa tinhlangano temathishela letintsatfu, naptosa, sadtu ne-saou, sekucinisa futsi nekutibophetela kwabo emkhankasweni wekufundza nekufundzisa lokusezingeni leliphakeme kusukela ekucaleni kwa-2010.
tsn: naptosa, sadtu le saou, foo ba neng ba boeletsa boitlamo jwa bona malebana le kgoeletso ya boleng jo bo kwa godimo jwa go ithuta le go ruta go simolola ka 2010. maloko a a tlotlegang,re tlhoka go beeletsa mo basweng go tlhomamisa gore re nna le mophato wa badiri o o nang le bokgoni jwa go tshegetsa kgolo le tlholego ya ditiro.

ssw: malunga lahloniphekile,kumele sisise kulusha lwetfu kute sicinisekise kutsi sinetisebenti letinemakhono naletikwatiko kusebenta kute kwesekelwe kukhula nekusungulwa kwemisebenti.
tsn: ka jalo, re rulaganyetsa go oketsa le go godisa katiso ya baswa ba dingwaga di le 16-25 malebana le ditirelo tsa thuto le katiso e e tswelelang.

ssw: ngaloko sihlela kwandzisa kuceceshwa kwalabaneminyaka yebudzala lengu-16-25 etikhungweni temfundvo nekucecesha.
tsn: se, se tla re kgontsha go neela baithuti ba ba sa lekanelang yunibesithi, tshono ya go rutega.

ssw: loku kutasenta sikwati kuniketa imfundvo litfuba lesibili, kulabo labangakulungeli kuya emanyuvesi.
tsn: re dira mmogo le ditheo tsa thuto e kgolwane go netefatsa gore baithuti ba ba nang le tshwanelo ya go amogelwa, ba bona thuso ya madi, ka mosele wa sekema sa setshaba sa thuso ya matlole sa baithuti.

ssw: sisebentisana netikhungo temfundvo lephakeme kute kucinisekiswe kutsi bafundzi labakulungele batfola lusito lwetimali, ngeluhlelo lwavelonkhe lwekusita bafundzi ngetimali.
tsn: re beile dintlhaphitlhelelo tsa maemogodimo tsa tlhabololo ya bokgoni, go oketsa palo ya baenjenere le bategeniki, le go oketsa palo ya barutabana ba ba nonofileng ba mmetse mmogo le bonetetshi.

ssw: siphindze satibekela emanani ekutfutfukiswa kwemakhono, kute kukhicitwe labanye bonjiniyela nabochwepheshe, kuphindze kwenyuswe linani labothishela labakufanele kufundzisa tibalo nesayensi.
tsn: re tshwanetse ra oketsa le palo ya baswa ba ba tsenelang dithutela tirong mo maphateng a poraefete mmogo le a puso.

ssw: kumele futsi senyuse linani lalabasha labangenela tinhlelo tekufundza ngemisebenti emikhakheni letimele nasemkhakheni wahulumende.
tsn: poelo nngwe ya botlhokwa ke go netefatsa botshelo jo boleele jwa boitekanelo gommaaforika borwa otlhe.

ssw: sitawuchubeka nekwenta ncono luhlelo lwetfu lwetemphilo.
tsn: re tla tswelela go tokafatsa thulaganyo ya rona ya tlhokomelo ya boitekanelo.

ssw: loku kufaka ekhatsi kulungisa tibhedlela nemitfolamphilo, kanye nekwenta ncono timo tekusebenta tetisebenti tetemphilo.
tsn: se se akaretsa kago le tlhabololo ya dikokelo le ditleliniki, mmogo le tokafatso ya maemo a tiro a badiri ba tlhokomelo ya boitekanelo.

ssw: sibambisene nelibhange lekutfutfukisa le-afrika leseningizimu kute kwentiwe ncono kusebenta kwetibhedlela temmango kanye nemahhovisi ato etifundza.
tsn: re utlwanetse bolekane le bankatlhabololo ya borwa jwa aforika, malebana le go tokafatsa bodiredi jwa dikokelo tsa puso mmogo le dikantoro tsa dikgaolo.

ssw: siphindze sisebentisane nelibhange lekutfutfukisa le-afrika leseningizimu kanye nenhlangano letfutfukisa timboni, eluhlelweni lwebudlelwane kuhulumende nalabatimele kute kwentiwe ncono tibhedlela kanye nekusita imiklamo ngetimali.
tsn: re bile re dirisana le bankatlhabololo ya aforika borwa (dbsa) mmogo le koporasi ya tsweletso ya madirelo.

ssw: malunga lahloniphekile,kumele sibukane nekutsi umjikeleto wemphilo kusukela esikhatsini sekutalwa, wehle kusukela eminyakeni lengama-60 nga-1994 kuye wufinyelela ngephansi kweminyaka lengama-50 lamuhla.
tsn: tirisano ya rona e ka mananeo a motlhakanelwa a puso-poraefete, go tlhabolola dikokelo le go aba matlole go diporojeke.

ssw: ngako siyangenelela ngenhloso yekunciphisa emazinga ekufa kwebantfwana lababelekwako, kute kuncishiswe kwesuleleka ngesandvulelangculazi lokusha kanye nekwelashwa kwesandvulelangculazi nesifo sesifuba ngalokuyimphumelelo.
tsn: ka jalo, re tshwaragane le go tsereganya go fokotsa kelo ya dintsho tse di tlholwang ke pelegi, go fokotsa phetetso ya hiv mmogo le go alafa hiv le lohuba.

ssw: sitawuphindze sinciphise kufa kwetinswane ngeluhlelo lwekugonywa kwetinswane letinyenti.
tsn: re ya go fokotsa dintsho tsa masea ka tiriso ya mananeo a a kwenneng a moento.

ssw: sitawubuyisela tinhlelo tetemphilo etikolweni.
tsn: re ya go busa mananeo a tsa boitekanelo kwa dikolong.

ssw: sitakwenta tonkhe tetsembiso lesatenta ngelusuku lwengculazi lwemhlabawonkhe letimayelana netindlela letinsha tekuvikela nekwelapha sandvulelangculazi.
tsn: re ya go diragatsa maitlamo otlhe a a tserweng ka letsatsi la lefatshe la aids, maitlamo a a amanang le mekgwa e meswa ya thibelo le kalafo ya hiv.

ssw: umsebenti uyachubeka kute kucinisekiswe kutsi umsebenti uhambisana nesikhatsi lesibekiwe.
tsn: re tshwaragane le tiro e e makitla go netefatsa gore tiro e, e diragala mo nakong e e utlwanetsweng.

ssw: sitawuphindze sichubeke nemalungiselelo ekusungula luhlelo lwemshwalense wetemphilo velonkhe.
tsn: re tla tswelela le ka paakanyetso ya go tlhomiwa ga thulaganyo ya puso ya insorense ya bosetshaba ya boitekanelo.

ssw: takhamiti taseningizimu afrika,sisebenta kamatima kucinisekisa kutsi wonkhe umuntfu eningizimu afrika utiva aphephile kanye nekutsi kuphephile.
tsn: maaforika borwa a gaetsho,re dira ka natla go netefatsa gore mongwe le mongwe mo aforika borwa o ikutlwa a babalesegile le gore o babalesegile.

ssw: sitawuchubekisela embili umsebenti wetfu wekunciphisa bugebengu lobukhulu nalobuneludlame, siphindze sicinisekise kutsi luhlelo lwetebulungiswa lusebenta kahle.
tsn: re ya go tsweletsa tiro ya rona go fokotsa bokebekwa jo bogolo, le go netefatsa gore thulaganyo ya bosiamisi e dira ka tolamo.

ssw: setfula tinhlelo tekwenyusa linani lemaphoyisa ngemaphesenti lalishumi kuleminyaka lemitsatfu letako.
tsn: re tsenya tirisong dithulaganyo tsa go oketsa palo ya mapodisi ka 10% mo dingwageng tse tharo tse di latelang.

ssw: sikhombe kulwa nekutsatselwa timoto, kwebelwa kwemabhizimisi netindlu, kanye nebugebengu lobenteka ngekutsintsana lobunjengekubulala, kuhlukumeta ngekwelucansi kanye nekushaya, njengetintfo letisetulu eluhlwini lwetintfo letibalulekile.
tsn: re lemogile le go tlhaola jaaka ditlapele, ntwa kgatlhanong le go thopiwa ka dikgoka, thukutho ya mafelokgwebo le matlo, mmogo le bonokwane bo tshwana le polao, petelelo le kgobatso.

ssw: sonkhe sinendzima lokumele siyidlale.
tsn: rotlhe re tshwanetse go nna le seabe.

ssw: asitibandzakanye netinkhundla temmango letibukene nekuphepha.
tsn: a re tseeng karolo mo ditheong tsa pabalesego tsa motse.

ssw: asesiyekele kutsenga timphahla letintjontjiwe.
tsn: a re leseng go reka dithoto tsa bogodu.

ssw: asilungele kuniketa emaphoyisa lwati lolumayelana netento tebugebengu.
tsn: a ka gale re nne re ipaakanyeditse go neela mapodisi tshedimosetso ka ga bosenyi.

ssw: ngekusebentisana sitabehlula bugebengu.
tsn: fa re dirisana re tla fenya bosenyibakaulengwe le baeng ba tlotlego,pusoselegae e tshwanetse go dira.

ssw: bomasipala kumele bente ncono kuniketelwa kwetindlu, emanti, tekuhanjiswa kwemangcoliso, gezi, kutfutfwa kwetibi kanye nemigwaco.
tsn: bommasepala ba tshwanetse go tokafatsa thebolo ya matlo, metsi, kgeleloleswe, motlakase, taolo ya matlakala le ditsela.

ssw: sibambe umhlangano nabosodolobha kanye nebaphatsi babomasipala emnyakeni lowengcile.
tsn: re tsene pitso le bommeiyara le balaodi ba mmasepala ngogola.

ssw: loku kunikete litfuba lekubona tintfo letingabonakali ngetincabhayi lebanato bohulumende basekhaya.
tsn: pitso e e re neetse tshedimosetso e e boteng malebana le dikgwetlho tse di fitlhelwang mo pusoselegaeng.

ssw: siphindze savakashela imimango nabomasipala labehlukehlukene, kufaka ekhatsi ibalfour empumalanga kanye nethembisa egauteng.
tsn: re bile re etetse merafe le bommasepala ba ba farologaneng, go akarediwa balfour kwa mpumalanga mmogo le thembisa kwa gauteng.

ssw: ngemuva kwekuvakashela ebalfour, sitfumele litsimba lemalunga layimfica etindvuna kutsi avakashele lendzawo kute ayewubukana netindzaba letiphakanyiswe ngummango.
tsn: morago ga ketelo ya balfour re rometse setlhopha sa ditona di le robongwe go etela kgaolo e ya balfour go mekamekana le dintlha tse di tlhagisitsweng ke baagi.

ssw: tindzaba letinyenti setivele tiyabukisiswa.
tsn: dintlha dingwe di setse di tsibogetswe.

ssw: ngiyalele tindvuna kutsi tibukane netindzaba letisasele.
tsn: ke laetse ditona go tlhokomela dintlha tse di saletseng morago.

ssw: sisasho futsi kutsi atikho tikhalo letivumela ludlame nekucekelwa phansi kwemphahla.
tsn: re gatelela gore ga go dingongorego dipe tse di fiwang jaaka lebaka la borukhutlhi le tshenyo ya dithoto.

ssw: siyalele tikhungo letibukene nekulandzelwa kwemtsetfo kutsi titsatse tinyatselo leticinile kulabo labangahloniphi umtsetfo ebalfour nakuletinye tindzawo.
tsn: re laetse badiredi ba semolao gore ba gagamatse ditomo mo botlhokataolong jwa kwa balfour le dikarolo tse dingwe.

ssw: ngengongoni 2009, ikhabinethi ivume lisu lekugucula kusebenta kwetintfo kubohulumende basekhaya.
tsn: ka sedimonthole 2009, kabinete e atlanegisitse togamaano ya semenogane ya pusoselegae.

ssw: loku kutawucinisekisa kutsi bohulumende basekhaya banebuphatsi lobufanele, nemakhono ekuphatsa kanye newebuchwepheshe.
tsn: se se tla netefatsa gore pusoselegae e na le bolaodi jo bo maleba mmogo le bokgoni jwa tsamaiso le setegeniki.

ssw: kulomnyaka wekwenta, asibambisaneni ekwenteni bohulumende basekhaya babe ngumsebenti wakhe wonkhe umuntfu.
tsn: mo ngwageng ono wa tiro, a re direng mmogo go netefatsa gore kwa bofelong, pusoselegae e nna tiro ya rona rotlhe.

ssw: sisebentela kwenta ncono tindzawo tekuhlala letingakahleleki kanye nekuniketela ngetinsita letifanele kanye nebunini bemhlaba lokungenani kumakhaya langu-500 000 nga-2014.
tsn: re tshwaragane le go tlhabolola mekhukhu mmogo le go tlhoma ditirelo tse di tlhamatsegang go bonnye jwa malapa a le 500 000 ka 2014. re rulaganya go beela thoko dihekethara di feta 6 000 tsa naga ya puso e e mo felong go isegang, go aga matlo a a tlhwatlwa tlase.

ssw: sihlela kubekela eceleni emahektha langetulu kwa-6 000 emhlaba losedvutane nemmango kute kwakhiwe kuwo tindlu talabahola kancane naletingabiti kakhulu.
tsn: maitlhomomagolo a maswa e ya go akaretsa batho ba lotseno lwa bona lo leng kwa godimo foo lo ba rontshang go amogela ketleetso ya puso, le gale lotseno lo lo le kwa tlase ga kelo ya go bona ketleetso ya dibanka.

ssw: umtamo lomusha loyinsika kutawuba kucabangela bantfu labahola kakhulu kute batfole kusitwa ngetimali nguhulumende, kodvwa lokubonakala bahola kancane ngendlela yekutsi abakulungeli kusitwa ngemabhange kutsi batsenge tindlu.
tsn: re ya go tlhoma ketleetso ya r1 bilione go tlhotlha dibanka tsa poraefete mmogo le lekala la matlo go aga dikumo go tlhokomela kgwetlho e ya matlo.

ssw: bakitsi,emnyakeni lowengcile sitsite, bantfu basemakhaya nabo banelilungelo lekuba nagezi, emanti, imithoyi lehanjiswa ngemanti kanye nemigwaco.
tsn: bakaulengwe, mo ngwageng o o fetileng re rile baagi ba metsemagae le bona ba na le tshwanelo ya go nna le motlakase, metsi, matlwana a metsi mmogo le ditsela.

ssw: satsi kumele babe netindzawo tetemidlalo kanye netindzawo letinetitolo tekutsenga letinkhulu letincono njengaleto tasemadolobheni.
tsn: ra re ba tshwanetse go nna le ditikwatikwe tsa metshameko gammogo le tsa marekelo jaaka kwa ditoropong.

ssw: kuloku, sisukumise indzawo yekucala lokutawuhlolwa kuyo luhlelo loluphelele lwekutfutfukisa tindzawo tasemakhaya egiyani, elimpopo, ngengci emnyakeni lowengcile.
tsn: malebana le se, re itsisitse ketelelafelo ya lenaneo tlhabololo kakaretso la magae kwa giyani, limpopo, ka phatwe ngogola.

ssw: kusukela ngaleso sikhatsi, sekwakhiwe tindlu letingama-231.
tsn: go tloga motsi o, go agilwe matlo a le 231. go nnile le tswelopele mo neelong ya ditirelo go tshegetsa tlhabololo ya tsa temo, mmogo le katiso ya ditokololo tsa morafe.

ssw: kufinyelela etikhungweni tetemphilo netemfundvo kwentiwe ncono.
tsn: phitlhelelo ya ditirelo tsa boitekanelo le thuto e tokafetse.

ssw: senta tinhlelo letinjengaleto etindzaweni letisikhombisa eliveni lonkhe, letizuzisa emawadi langu-21.
tsn: re diragatsa mananeo a mofuta o mo mafelong a le supa mo nageng.

ssw: nga-2014, sihlose kuba netindzawo letinjalo kumawadi langu-160.
tsn: mananeo a a tla tswela mosola dikgaolotlhopho di le 21. fa 2014 o rogwa, re ikaelela go nna le mafelo mo dikgaolotlhophong di le 160. re eletsa gore 60% ya malapa mo mafelong a e kgone go fitlhelela ditlhokego tsa bona tsa dijo go tswa dikumong tsaabo ka ngwaga wa 2014. kgato ka kgato re tla bo re fitlhe jaaka seane se re bakaulengwe, dilo tse kgolo di simolola ka dikgato tse dinnye.

ssw: kumele futsi sihlanganise kancono tinhlelo teluhlelobusha lwemhlabatsi kanye netinhlelo letesekela tekulima.
tsn: re lebanwe gape ke go nyalana mananeo tshegetso a tlhabololo ya naga mmogo le temo.

ssw: imphumelelo yetfu kulomkhakha itawukalwa ngekwenyuka kwelinani lebalimi labalima etindzaweni letincane labagcina sebakwati kutimela kutemnotfo.
tsn: mo karolong e katlego ya rona e tla lekanyetswa ka koketsego ya palo ya balemipotlana ba ba nnang balemibagolo.

ssw: somlomo lohloniphekile nasihlalo wemkhandlu wetifundza wavelonkhe,asisilo live lelinemanti lamanyenti.
tsn: motlotlegi mmusakgotla le modulasetulo wa lekgotla la bosetshaba la diporofense,naga ya rona ga e a huma ka metsi.

ssw: kodvwa sisalahlekelwa ngemanti lamanyenti ngemaphayiphi lavutako nangesakhiwonchanti lesingakalungi.
tsn: le fa go le jalo, re latlhegelwa ke metsi a le mantsi ka ntata ya dipeipe tse di dutlang le dipopotheo tse di sa lekanelang.

ssw: sitawube sibeka tindlela tekunciphisa kulahlekela kwetfu ngemanti ngelinani lelinguhhafu nga-2014.
tsn: re ya go bopa maano a go fokotsa tatlhegelo ya metsi ka seripa fa 2014 a rogwa.

ssw: malunga lahloniphekile,njengencenye yemitamo yetfu yekukhutsata kukhula kutemnotfo, sisebentela kunciphisa tindleko tekuchumana.
tsn: maloko a a tlotlegang,jaaka karolo ya maiteko a rona a go rotloetsa kgolo ya ikonomi, re dira ka natla go fokotsa ditshenyegelo tsa tlhaeletsano.

ssw: ummango weleningizimu afrika ungabuka embili kulokunye futsi kunciphisa ngalokubanti, emanani abomakhalekhikhini, lucingo lwasendlini kanye netincingo temmango.
tsn: morafe wa aforika borwa o ka solofela phokotso ya kelo ya tlhotlhwa ya go dirisa mogala wa selefounu, wa fa gae mmogo le wa botlhe.

ssw: sitawusebentela kwenyusa sivinini siphindze sicinisekise emazinga lasetulu etinhlelo te-intanethi, ngekuhambisana nenkhambiso yemave emhlaba.
tsn: re ya go dira ka natla go oketsa lebelo la kgolagano, ka maikaelelo a go netefatsa maemogodimo a tirelo ya ditirelo tsa inthanete, re inaakantse le moono wa boditshabatshaba.

ssw: takhamiti teleningizimu afrika,lohulumende utawucinisekisa kutsi imphahla yendalo netinsita letitfolakala endalweni tivikeleke kahle, nekutsi tiyachubeka nekukhuliswa.
tsn: maaforika borwa a gaetsho, puso e ya go netefatsa gore dithoto tsa rona tsa tikologo mmogo le madirelo a tlhago di a tlhokomelwa le go atlarelwa ka gale.

ssw: ngekubambisana nelebrazil, indiya nechina, kuhlanganisa nelemelika, lemele emave latfutfukile, sifake ligalelo lelivakalako ekwemukelweni kwesivumelwano emhlanganweni wekugucuka kwesimo selitulu wasecopenhagen ngengongoni kulomyaka lowengcile.
tsn: re akgetse go bonala malebana le tumallano e e amogetsweng kwa pitsokgolong ya phetogo ya tlelaemete ya copenhagen ka sedimonthole ngogola, re na le dinaga tsa brazil, india le china, mmogo le united states e e neng e emetse dinaga tse di tlhabologileng.

ssw: nanobe kungakefiki lapho kudzingeka khona, kodvwa kusinyatselo lesibalulekile njengobe onkhe emave aphendvula kulokugucuka kwesimo selitulu.
tsn: le fa tumallano e e sa fitlha fa re neng re solofetse, e nnile kgato ya botlhokwa ka gobo e bofa dinaga tsotlhe go tsibogela phetogo ya tlelaemete.

ssw: sitawusebenta ngemandla nebalingani betfu bemave emhlaba ngenhloso yekufinyelela esivumelwaneni lesibophako nalesisemtsefweni.
tsn: re ya go dira ka natla go gaisa mmogo le balekane ba rona ba boditshabatshaba malebana le maitlamo a semolao.

ssw: njengeningizimu afrika, sitibophetele ngekutitsandzela emananini lesitibekele wona ekunciphisa kungcoliswa kwemoya, kantsi sitawuchubeka nekusebentela kuhlangabetana nendlelasu yetfu yesikhatsi lesidze yekunciphisa kugucuka kwesimo selitulu.
tsn: mo aforika borwa re itlametse ntlhaphitlhelelo ya phokotsotsweletso e e rileng mme re ya go tswelela go dira ka natla malebana le maano a rona a tsereganyo ya phetogo ya leruri ya tlelaemete.

ssw: malunga lahloniphekile,sitawucinisa imitamo yetfu yekuchubekisela embili tinhloso teningizimu afrika emhlabeni wonkhe.
tsn: maloko a a tlotlegang,re ya go nonotsha maitlhomo a go godisa dikgatlhegelo tsa aforika borwa mo lefatsheng ka bophara.

ssw: sitawesekela imitamo yekunonophisa kuhlangana kutembusave nakutemnotfo kwesifundza se-sadc, kanye nekukhutsata kuhwebelana nekusisa emkhatsini kwemave akulesifundza.
tsn: re tla tshegetsa maiteko a go oketsa lebelo la go nyalanya dinaga tsa sadc malebana le polotiki le ikonomi, mmogo le go rotloetsa kgwebo le peeletso magareng a dinaga tse.

ssw: iningizimu afrika iyachubeka nekudlala indzima lesembili emitameni yelivekati kute kuciniswe lubumbano lwe-afrika netinhlaka talo, kanye nekusebentela bunye.
tsn: aforika borwa e tswelela go nna moeteledipele mo maitekong a go natlafatsa kitlano ya aforika mmogo le makala a yona go direla kopano.

ssw: sitawugcila kutemandla ekuniketeni kabusha emandla budlelwane lobusha bekutfutfukiswa kwe-afrika, njengendlelasu yekutfutfukisa temnotfo kulelivekati.
tsn: re ya go tsepamisa maatla mo tsosolosong ya semphatho se se ntshwa sa tlhabololo ya aforika jaaka maano a tlhabololo ya ikonomi ya kontinente.

ssw: takhamiti teleningizimu afrika,umsebenti wahulumende kumele usabele elubitweni lwekwenta lesigamu sibe ngulesinye sekusebenta ngekunonopha kanye nekusebenta kwembuso lokwentiwe ncono.
tsn: maaforika borwa a gaetsho,bodiredipuso bo tshwanela ke go tsibogela kgoeletso e go dira gore paka e e nne ya tiro e e potlakileng le go tokafatsa tiragatso ya puso.

ssw: sidzinga kusebenta ngalokuncomekako nangemandla.
tsn: re lebeletse manontlhotlho le go dira ka natla.

ssw: sidzinga tisebenti tahulumende letitimisele, letinemakhono naletinakekela tidzingo tetakhamiti.
tsn: re tlhoka badiredipuso ba ba ineetseng, ba ba kgonang mme barekegela ditlhokwa tsa baagi.

ssw: hulumende sewuvele usebentela ekutfutfukiseni nasekwetfuleni luhlelo lwekutfutfukisa umsebenti wahulumende, lolutawubeka inkhambiso necophelo etisebentini tahulumende kuyo yonkhe imikhakha.
tsn: puso e setse e dira ka tlhabololo le go tsenya tirisong mananeo a tlhabololo ya badiredi puso a a yang go ala motheo wa badiredi puso mo mefameng yotlhe.

ssw: malunga lahloniphekile,sichubekisa imitamo yetfu yekucedza inkhohlakalo nekweba eluhlelweni lwekuniketwa kwemisebenti nemathenda, naseticelweni tetincwadzi tekushayela, kutibonelelo tahulumende nakubomatisi, phakatsi kwalokunye.
tsn: maloko a a tlotlegang,re tsweletsa maiteko a rona a go fedisa bomenemene le botsietsi mo tsamaisong ya dithendara mmogo le mo dikopong tsa makwalokgweetso, madi a tlamelo a puso le makwalo ikitsiso gareng ga tse dingwe.

ssw: siyajabula ngenchubekelembili hulumende lasayentile kuleminye imikhakha.
tsn: re motlotlo ka tema e puso e e beileng mo dikarolong dingwe.

ssw: kuleliviki, sicedze kukhokhelwa kwetibonelelo tahulumende letinenkhohlakalo letingu-32 687, letibita imali lengemarandi latigidzi letingu-180.
tsn: mo bekeng e, re khutlisitse tuelo ya madi a tlamelo a puso a bomenemene go batho ba le 32 687. madi a a lekanyetswa go dimilione di le r180.

ssw: likomiti letindvuna lelibukene nenkhohlakalo lisabuka tindlela tekucedza nya inkhohlakalo.
tsn: komiti ya rona ya ditona, e e lebileng bomenemene, e sekaseka tsela ya leruri ya go fenya bomenemene.

ssw: ngekusebentisana singenta lokunyenti.
tsn: fa re dirisana re ka fitlhelela go le gontsintsi.

ssw: bakitsi,njengobe nati, setfule inombolo yekutsintana nelihhovisi lamengameli kute sente hulumende nelihhovisi lamengameli lifinyeleleke kummango, kanye nekusita kuvulela kweftulwa kwetinsita letivalelekile.
tsn: bakaulengwe,jaaka lo lemogile, re itsisitse mogala o o kgethegileng wa moporesidente gore puso mmogo le kantoro ya moporesidente di fitlhelelwe bonolo ke setshaba le go thibolola thebolelo ya ditirelo.

ssw: lenombolo yamengameli imele kutimisela kwetfu ekwenteni tintfo kuhulumende ngalokwehlukile.
tsn: mogala o o kgethegileng ke sekai sa maikaelelo a rona a go dira dilo ka tsela e e farologaneng mo pusong.

ssw: kwente umehluko etimphilweni tetakhamiti letinyenti teleningizimu afrika.
tsn: se se tlhodile phetogo mo matshelong a bontsi jwa baagi ba aforika borwa.

ssw: buziwe ngaleka wasemount frere, lowaba nesicelo sekucala lesasitsatsa lebesimayelana nemphesheni yemyeni wakhe longasekho, lolu kwaba lucingo lolwatsatfwa elusukwini lwekucala kwekusebenta kwalenombolo.
tsn: re ka bolela ka leina mohumagadi buziwe ngaleka wa kwa mount frere yo o nnileng motho wa ntlha go letsetsa mogala o a ngongorega ka tsamaiso ya phensene ya moswi mogatse.

ssw: nkululeko cele, lowasitwa kutfola tincwadzi tamatisi, lokwamenta wakwati kubhalisa enyuvesi yethekhinoloji yasetshwane.
tsn: re na gape fano le rre nkululeko cele, yo o neng a thusega go bona lekwalo ikitsiso le le mo kgontshitseng go ikwadisa kwa yunibesithing ya tshwane ya thekenoloji.

ssw: leti tindzaba letimbili nje kuphela temphumelelo emkhatsini kwaletinyenti.
tsn: tse ke dikanelo di le pedi fela, gareng ga bontsi jwa dikanelo tse di supileng katlego.

ssw: kuleti naletinye tibonelo, sibona butsakatsaka lokumele bulungiswe tinhlaka tahulumende letahlukahlukene.
tsn: go tswa dikaong tse mmogo le tse dingwe re lemoga makoa a a tshwanetseng go baakangwa ke mefama e e farologaneng ya puso.

ssw: ngasomlomo, simeme titfunywa temacembu lahlukene ephalamende kutsi avakashele sikhungo setincingo, kute emalunga ephalamende atotibonela umsebenti lowentiwako.
tsn: ka tiriso ya mmusakgotla re laleditse boemedi jwa makokomantsi go tswa palamenteng go etela lefelo la mogala o gore ditokololo tsa palamente di itemogele bogolo jwa tiro e e dirwang koo.

ssw: bakitsi nebangani,ngichaze tincenye letimbalwa teluhlelo lwetfu lwa-2010, kutibophetela kwetfu sisonkhe njengahulumende kubantfu beleningizimu.
tsn: bakaulengwe le ditsala,ke tlhalositse dintlhakgolo tsa thulaganyo ya rona ya 2010 e bong maitlamo a rona a motlhakanelwa jaaka puso go baagi ba aforika bowa.

ssw: inkhulumo leyetfulelwa sive iniketa sibutsetelo lesibanti seluhlelo lwetfu lwekwenta.
tsn: puo ya maemo a setshaba a neela tebokakaretso ya thulaganyo ya rona ya tiro.

ssw: tindvuna titawuniketa umbiko lowenabile ngalesikhatsi tetfula tinkhulumo tawo temcombelelotimali.
tsn: ditona di tla neela diteng ka nako ya tsona ya puo ya boutu ya tekanyetso.

ssw: malunga lahloniphekile, takhamiti teleningizimu afrika,ngelweti kulomnyaka, sitawube sigubha umnyaka wa-150 wekufika kwemandiya eningizimu afrika.
tsn: maloko a a tlotlegang,maaforika borwa a gaetsho, ka kgwedi ya ngwanatsele monongwaga re tla bo re keteka dingwaga di le 150 go tloga motsi wa kgorogo ya maintia mo aforika borwa.

ssw: kuniketa litfuba lekubona kubaluleka kwesandla lesifakwe ngummango wemandiya emikhakheni yetemisebenti, temabhizimisi, tesayensi, temidlalo, tenkholo, tebuciko, temasiko kanye nasekutfolweni nasekuhlanganisweni kwentsandvo yetfu yelinyenti.
tsn: se se re neela tshono ya go lemoga seabe sa botlhokwa sa morafe wa maintia mo dikarolong tsa bodiri, kgwebo, bonetetshi, metshameko, tumedi, botsweretshi, setso le katlego mmogo le tiiseletso ya demokerasi ya rona.

ssw: bakitsi nebangani,asengitsatse lelitfuba ngiphindze ngendlulise emavi endvudvuto kuhulumende kanye nebantfu basehaiti ngenhlekelele nekufa lokubuhlungu lokubavelele.
tsn: bakaulengwe le ditsala,nte ke dirise tshono eno go boa ke isa matshediso a rona go tswa botennye jwa pelo go puso mmogo le baagi ba haiti ka masetlapelo a dira-ga-di-bonwe a a ba wetseng.

ssw: siyajabula kutsi litsimba lebasiti betfu likwatile kuyewusita.
tsn: re motlotlo gobo ditlhopha tsa rona tsa pholoso di kgonne go ya go thusa.

ssw: ngitsandza kubonga sakhamuti seleningizimu afrika lesihlala singahluleki kusita njalo etikhatsini tetinhlekelele, siphindze sisite tsine ekukhuliseni umbono wekuba ngummango lonakekelako.
tsn: ke rata mo nakong eno go lemoga le go amogela moaforika yo ka gale a sa itsapeng go thusa mo dinakong tsa matlhotlhapelo a tshwana le a. moaforika yo o thusa go godisa maitlhomo a morafe o o tlhokomelang.

ssw: imtiaz sooliman we-gift of the givers lesinaye lapha lamuhla.
tsn: re amogela fano mo ntlung e ngaka imtiaz sooliman wa gift of the givers.

ssw: bakitsi beleningizimu afrika,kubanjwa kwemidlalo yendzebe yemhlaba ye-fifa kwenta 2010 abe ngumnyaka wekwenta mbamba.
tsn: maaforika borwa a gaetsho,go nna bengae ba sejana sa lefatshe sa fifa go dira gore 2010 e nne ngwaga wa tiro ga mmannete.

ssw: sichitse iminyaka leminyenti sihlelela lendzebe yemhlaba.
tsn: re feditse dingwaga re rulaganyetsa sejana se sa lefatshe.

ssw: sisalelwe tinyanga letintsatfu kuphela.
tsn: re setse fela ka dikgwedi di le tharo.

ssw: kantsi sitimisele kwenta lemidlalo ibe yimphumelelo.
tsn: re itomile sesino gore sejana se se atlege.

ssw: sakhiwonchanti, tekuvikeleka kanye naletinye tinhlelo setikhona kute kucinisekiswe umchudzelwano loyimphumelelo.
tsn: dipopotheo, tshireletso mmogo le dintsanantsana tsa paakanyetso di rulagantswe go netefatsa katlego ya metshameko e ya kgwele dinao.

ssw: njengesive, kumele sibonge likomiti leligcugcutelela imidlalo ya-2010 ngemtamo wabo lomuhle.
tsn: morafe otlhe o isa malebogo a boikokobetso go komiti ya dithulaganyo ya selegae ka matsapa a bona.

ssw: sifisela sihlalo welikomiti leligcugcutelela lemidlalo, irvin khoza, sikhulu lesisetulu danny jordaan kanye nemceceshi webafana bafana, carlos alberto parreira, konkhe lokuhle kuletinyanga letilandzelako.
tsn: re eleletsa masego modulasetulo wa komiti e, irvin khoza, motlhankedimogolo danny jordaan mmogo le mokatisi wa bafana bafana carlos alberto parreira mo dikgweding di le mmalwa tse di tlang.

ssw: mengameli mandela bekasembili ekusiteni lelive kutsi litfole emalungelo ekubamba lomdlalo lomkhulu nakangaka.
tsn: moporesidente nelson mandela o nnile pinagare mo go tshegetseng naga e go nna le tshono ya go nna mongae wa tiragalo e kgolo e. ka jalo re tshwanetse go netefatsa gore sejana se sa lefatshe se atlega thata go tlotlomatsa nelson mandela.

ssw: ngako kumele sente lendzebe yemhlaba ibe yimphumelelo kute sihloniphe yena.
tsn: bakaulengwe a re nneng mowa mongwe go ema setlhopha sa naga bafana bafana nokeng.

ssw: sonkhe asitsengeni emathikithi kusenesikhatsi kute sikwati kuhambela lemidlalo.

ssw: 13 feb 2014somlomo lohloniphekile welibandla lavelonkhe,sihlalo wemkhandlu wetifundza wavelonkhe (ncop).
tsn: 13 feb 2014mmusakgotla yo o tlotlegang wa kokoanotheomolao ya bosetšhaba,modulasetulo wa lekgotla la bosetšhaba la diporofense (ncop).

ssw: sekela somlomo welibandla lavelonkhe nasekela sihlalo wemkhandlu wetifundza wavelonkhe.
tsn: motlatsammusakgotla wa kokoanotheomolao ya bosetšhaba le motlatsamodulasetulo wa ncop.

ssw: sekela mengameli weriphabhulikhi yeningizimu afrika, mhlonishwa kgalema motlanthe.
tsn: motlatsamoporesitente wa rephaboliki, motlotlegi kgalema motlanthe.

ssw: sekela mengameli wangaphambilini baleka mbethe,mhlonishwa jaji lelikhulu leriphabhulikhi yeningizimu afrika, nani nonkhe malunga lahloniphekile etebulungiswa.
tsn: motlatsamoporesitente wa maloba, baleka mbethe,motlotlegi moatlhodimogolo wa rephaboliki, le ditokololo tsotlhe tse di tlotlegang tsa bosiamisi.

ssw: tindvuna letihloniphekile nabosekela tindvuna,tindvuna tetifundza letikhetsekile nabosomlomo betifundza tetfu.
tsn: ditona le batlatsatona ba ba tlotlegang,ditonakgolo tse di tlotlegang le babusakgotla ba diporofense tsa rona.

ssw: sihlalo wenhlangano yabohulumende basekhaya eningizimu afrika, nabo bonkhe buholi babohulumende basekhaya.
tsn: modulasetulo wa mokgatlho wa dipusoselegae tsa aforika borwa, le boeteledipele jotlhe jwa pusoselegae.

ssw: sihlalo wendlu yavelonkhe yebaholi bendzabuko.

ssw: mphatsi welibhangesilulu,baholi bemabhizinisi, temidlalo, tendzabuko, tetenkholo nayo yonkhe leminye imikhakha,malunga emancusa akulamanye emave, tivakashi letikhetsekile naletihloniphekile,malunga lahloniphekile,bantfu bakitsi baseningizimu afrika,good evening, sanibonani, molweni, dumelang, riperile, ndimadekwana, goeienaand.
tsn: baeteledipele go tswa kwa maphateng a kgwebo, metshameko, setso, bodumedi le a mangwe otlhe fela,ditokololo tsa ditheo tsa sedipolomate, baeng ba ba kgethegileng e bile ba tlotlega,ditokololo tse di tlotlegang,maaforika borwa ka nna,good evening, sanibonani, molweni, dumelang, riperile, ndimadekwana, goeienaand.

ssw: ngitsandza kubonga tikhulu letengamele ngekungika lelitfuba lekutsi ngikhulume nebantfu baseningizimu afrika, kulomkhosi wekugcina wenkhulumo yebunjalo belive, lokungewesine webuholi bentsandvo yelinyenti.
tsn: ke rata go leboga batlhankedi ba tsamaiso ka tšhono eno ya go bua le batho ba aforika borwa, mo tiragalong eno ya puo ya bofelo ya maemo a setšhaba ya puso ya bone ya temokerasi.

ssw: ngitsandza kwendlulisa emavi etfu endvudvuto ngekushona kwemhlonishwa mnu.
tsn: ke rata go fetisa matshediso le kutlobotlhoko ya rona ka go tlhokafala ga motlotlegi ben skhosana, mongwe wa ditokololo tse di dirileng sebaka go gaisa le mongwe wa bagolwane ba ntlo eno e e tlotlegang e bile e kile ya nna tona ya rona ya maloba ya ditirelo tsa kgopololo.

ssw: sibuhlungu kakhulu ngekusishiya kwakhe ngekutuma.
tsn: re utlwisitswe botlhoko ke go tsamaya ga gagwe go go neng go sa lebelelwa.

ssw: sindlulisela kukhala kwetfu emndenini wakhe, nakumholi we-inkatha freedom party (ifp) shenge, kanye nawo onkhe emalunga e-ifp.
tsn: re rata go gomotsa balelapa la gagwe, gammogo le moeteledipele wa ifp, shenge, le ditokololo tsotlhe tsa ifp.

ssw: somlomo lohloniphekile,sihlalo lohloniphekile we-ncop,lena yinkhulumo yebunjalo belive yekucala leyetfulwa angekho mengameli wetfu longumsunguli, umhlonishwa nelson rolihlahla mandela.
tsn: mmusakgotla yo o tlotlegang,modulasetilo yo o tlotlegang wa ncop,seno ke puo ya ntlha ya maemo a setšhaba e e diragalang re se na le moporesidente wa rona wa ntlha, motlotlegi nelson rolihlahla mandela.

ssw: kusishiya kwakhe emhlabeni, ngembi nje kwekutsi kube yiminyaka lenge-20 yenkhululeko yetfu nentsandvo yelinyenti, kwabanga buhlungu lobukhulu kubantfu bakitsi nangesheya kweminyele yetfu.
tsn: go tlhokafala ga gagwe, pele fela ga ngwaga wa bo20 wa kgololesego le temokerasi ya rona, go utlwisitse batho ba rona le ba ba kwa ntle ga melelwane ya rona botlhoko jo bo seng kana ka sepe.

ssw: sitfola kudvudvuteka ekwatini kutsi madiba utawuhlala aphila njalo etinhlitiyweni tetfu, nekutsi futsi sinemsebenti wekuchubela embili umshiyandvuku wakhe.
tsn: re ikgomotsa ka kitso ya gore madiba o tla nna ka gale a le mo dipelong tsa rona, le gore re na le maikarabelo a go tsweletsa boswa jwa gagwe.

ssw: malunga lahloniphekile,live letfu likhicite emadvodza nebafati labakhetsekile, lababe baholi ngetikhatsi letimatima.
tsn: ditokololo tse di tlotlegang,naga ya rona e tlhagisitse banna le basadi ba ba gaisang, ba ba tlametseng ka boeteledipele mo dinakong tse di thata.

tsn: re gopola botlhe ba ba tlhokafetseng ka nako ya dikhuduego tse di neng di etleediwa ke mmuso ka dingwaga tsa bo1980 le 1990 kwa makeišeneng le kwa metseng ya rona ya kwa magaeng.

ssw: jabu ndlovu, umeleli wenyonyane yavelonkhe yalabasebenta ngetinsimbi yaseningizimu afrika (i-numsa), wadvutjulwa washona nga-1988 emgungundlovu kanye nendvodza yakhe jabulani nendvodzana yabo.
tsn: mme jabu ndlovu, moemedi wa maloba wa badiri wa mokgatlho wa bosetšhaba wa badirakatshipi ba aforika borwa, o ne a thuntshiwa ka 1988 kwa pietermaritzburg mmogo le mogatse jabulani le morwa wa bona.

ssw: semukela indvodzakati yabo luhle nendvodzana yabo, sanele, sibuye futsi sihloniphe yonkhe imindeni leyashonelwa ngulabatsandzekako bayo, kuwo wonkhe umkhakha wetepolitiki.
tsn: re amogela morwadie luhle le morwa, sanele, mme re tlotla malapa otlhe a a latlhegetsweng ke baratiwa ba ona, go ralala mekgatlho yotlhe ya sepolotiki.

ssw: somlomo lohloniphekile,sihlalo lohloniphekile we-ncop,sakhona kuncoba bonkhe lobo buhlungu besikhatsi lesengcile sabuye sakha ummango lomusha.
tsn: mmusakgotla yo o tlotlegang,modulasetilo yo o tlotlegang wa ncop,re kgonne go fenya kutlobotlhoko eo yotlhe ya maloba le go aga setšhaba se sentšhwa.

ssw: sesakhe tikhungo leticinile tentsandvo yelinyenti.
tsn: re agile ditheo tse di maatla tsa temokerasi.

ssw: siwungcwabile umbuso welubandlululo lobewungasiyo intsandvo yelinyenti, lobewungameleli, ugcilatana ukhohlakele futsi lebewusebentela lidlantana.
tsn: re fitlhile mmuso o e neng e se wa temokerasi, o o neng o se na kemedi, o gatelela e bile o le bobodu o o neng o direla ba le mmalwa fela.

ssw: sakhe hulumende wentsandvo yelinyenti longabandlululi ngekwebulili, ngekwebuhlanga, lotiphendvulelako ubuye umelele bonkhe bantfu baseningizimu afrika.
tsn: re tlhamile mmuso wa temokerasi o o kopaneng, o o sa tlhaoleng go ya ka lotso le fa e le ka bong, o o ikarabelang mo baemeding ba maaforika borwa otlhe.

ssw: sakhe intsandvo yelinyenti lebuswa ngumtsetfosisekelo lonemphumelo, lonetinhlaka tembuso letisebenta kahle kakhulu – sishayamtsetfo, sigungu lesiphetse netebulungiswa.
tsn: re na le temokerasi ya molaotheo e e tlhaga, e e nang le maphata a a dirang sentle a mmuso - kgotlapeomolao, bokhuduthamaga le boatlhodi.

ssw: sinetikhungo tahulumende letesekela intsandvo yelinyenti tibuye tivikele emalungelo etakhamiti.
tsn: re na le ditheo tsa karolo ya bo 9 tse di tshegetsang temokerasi le go sireletsa ditshwanelo tsa baagi.

ssw: inkhululeko nentsandvo yelinyenti nako kwakhe sikhala semmango lonemdlandla kanye nebetindzaba labakhululekile.
tsn: kgololesego le temokerasi gape di dirile gore go nne le baagi ba ba tlhabologileng mme ba le matlhagatlhaga mmogo le bobegakgang jo bo gololesegileng.

ssw: inkhululeko ibuye yaletsa kwekucala ngca, setsembiso sekulingana ngekwebulili.
tsn: gape kgololesego e tlisitse la ntlha, tsholofelo ya tekatekano ya bong.

ssw: kumelelwa kwabomake kutikhungo tahulumende kukhule kakhulu kusukela ekucaleni kwenkhululeko, futsi nekukhuliswa kwetinsitanchanti nako kuyabazuzisa bomake.
tsn: kemedi ya basadi mo ditheong tsa setšhaba e oketsegile thata fa e sa le go simologa kgololosego, mme le katoloso ya ditirelo tsa motheo e ungwela basadi.

ssw: onkhe lamagalelo ente iningizimu afrika yaba yindzawo lencono kakhulu kutsi kuhlalwe kuyo manje kunangaphambilini.
tsn: dintlha tseno tsotlhe di dirile gore aforika borwa e nne lefelo le le botoka go nna mo go lona ga jaana go feta jaaka e kile ya nna.

ssw: nanoma kunjalo, live letfu lisebukene netinselele tebuphuya, kungalingani nekungabi khona kwemisebenti, lesiloku sibukene nako.
tsn: fela naga ya rona e sa ntse e lebanwe ke dikgwetlho tse tharo tsa lehuma, go tlhoka tekatekano le botlhokatiro, tse re tswelelang go samagana natso.

ssw: kubukana naletinselele sekube nguyonantfo lebalulekile lekugcilwe kuyo yabo bonkhe buphatsi bentsandvo yelinyenti.
tsn: go samagana le dikgwetlho tseno e setse e le ntlha ya botlhokwa ya mebuso yotlhe ya temokerasi.

ssw: sikhetse kugcila etintfweni letisihlanu letihamba embili, temfundvo, temphilo, kulwa nebugebengu nenkhohlakalo, kutfutfukiswa kwetindzawo tasemaphandleni nekulungiswa kabusha kwemhlaba kanye nekwakha imisebenti lenesitfunti.
tsn: thuto, boitekanelo, ntwa kgatlhanong le bosenyi le bobodu, tlhabololo ya metseselegae le ntšhwafatso ya naga mmogo le go tlhama ditiro tse di seriti.

ssw: siphindze futsi sahlela kabusha umbuso kute kutfutfukiswe kusebenta.
tsn: gape re nopotse gore puso e tshwanetse go tokafatsa tiragatso.

ssw: sente imisebenti lemibili lemikhulu, kuhlela kwesikhatsi lesidze kanye nekulandzelela nekuhlola.
tsn: re tlhamile ditiro di le pedi tsa botlhokwa.

ssw: sisungule ikhomishini yekuhlela yavelonkhe lekhicite lesikhonkhwane luhlelo lwekutfutfukisa lwavelonkhe, lokuluhlelo lwalelive lwetenhlalo netemnotfo nalokungulokunye lokuzuziwe lokukhulu kwalohulumende wesine.
tsn: re tlhamile khomišene ya maano ya bosetšhaba e e tlhagisitseng leano la tlhabololo la bosetšhaba (ndp), letlhomeso la naga la ikonomi ya loago mme gape e le nngwe ya diphitlhelelo tse dikgolo tsa puso ya bone.

ssw: loluhlelo lubeka kabanti ngalokufanele sikwente kute sicedze buphuya, kukhulisa ematfuba emisebenti nekunciphisa kungalingani kungakefiki umnyaka wa-2030.
tsn: leano le tlhagisa se re tshwanetseng go se dira go fedisa lehuma, go oketsa ditiro le gore re bo re fokoditse go tlhoka tekatekano ka 2030. tekolo le tshekatsheko ya rona e supa gore ditirelo di le dintsi di tswelela go tokafala.

ssw: kulandzelela nekuhlola kwetfu kukhombisa kutsi tinsita letinyenti tiyachubeka nekuba ncono.
tsn: sekai, jaanong go tsaya nako e khutshwane go bona madi a tlamelo le makwaloitshupo.

ssw: kepha letinye letinyenti tisadzinga kusetjentwa lokuchubekako.
tsn: fela tse dingwe tse dintsi di sa ntse di tlhoka tiro ntsi.

ssw: ngitawetfula umbiko ngaloku lokusihlanu lokuhamba embili, ngitawucala ngetemnotfo.
tsn: ke tla bega ka ditlapele tse tlhano, ke simolola ka ikonomi.

ssw: ngalokusemkhatsini, umnotfo ukhule ngemaphesenthi lama-3,2 ngemnyaka kusuka nga-1994 kuya ku-2012 nanoma nje umnotfo bewubutsakatsaka emhlabeni wonkhe jikelele lokwabanga kutsi kulahleke imisebenti lesigidzi.
tsn: ka kakaretso, ikonomi e godile ka 3.2% ka ngwaga go tloga ka 1994 go ya go 2012 le fa gone go na le kwelotlase ya ikonomi e e bakileng tatlhegelo ya ditiro di le milione lefatshe ka bophara.

ssw: ngekusebentisana sonkhe njengahulumende, bemabhizinisi, tisebenti kanye nemkhakha wemmango, siwunakekele lomnotfo wate wavuka.
tsn: ka go dira mmogo jaaka puso, kgwebo, badiri le lephata la baagi, re tataisa ikonomi gore e itharabologelwe.

ssw: umcebo wavelonkhe, nawukalwa ngekwemkhicito lomkhulu wasekhaya (gdp), ukhule waba ngetulu kwa-3,5wetigidzigidzi letiphindvwe katsatfu temarandi.
tsn: khumo ya bosetšhaba, e e lekanyediwang go ya ka seelosotlhe sa ditlhagisiwa tsa naga (gdp), e godile go ya go feta madi a a kanaka r3.5 ditirilone.

ssw: imisebenti manje iyasungulwa futsi.
tsn: jaanong go tlhamiwa ditiro gape.

ssw: manje sekunebantfu labatigidzi leti-15 labasebentako, linani lelikhulu kakhulu lelike labakhona kulelive, futsi kulomnyaka lophelile kuvulwe imisebenti lenge-650 000, ngekuya kwelihhovisi lelubalobalo laseningizimu afrika.
tsn: ga jaana go na le batho ba le dimilione di le 15 ba ba nang le ditiro mo nageng, e leng palo e e kwa godimo go gaisa mo hisetoring ya rona, mme ngogola go tlhamilwe ditiro di feta 650 000 go ya ka lefapha la mananepalo la aforika borwa.

ssw: loku solo akusiko lokukahle ngalokwenele.
tsn: seno se sa ntse se sa kgotsofatse.

ssw: silinganisonani sekungacashwa solomane sisetulu.
tsn: seelo sa botlhokatiro se sa ntse se le kwa godimo.

ssw: kucashwa kwelusha eningizimu afrika kusachubeka nekuba yintfo leletsa kukhatsateka, njengoba kwenteka mhlaba wonkhe jikelele.
tsn: botlhokatiro jwa bašwa mo aforika borwa bo tswelapele go tshwenya, fela jaaka mo lefatsheng ka bophara.

ssw: sitsatsa tinyatselo letinyenti, letifaka ekhatsi umtsetfo wekukhutsata intsela yekucashwa lokhutsata bacashi kutsi bacashe tisebenti letilusha.
tsn: re tsaya dikgato di le mmalwa, go akarediwa molao wa ditshiamelo tsa lekgetho la bothapi le le rotloetsang bathapi go thapa ba bašwa jaaka badiri.

ssw: kutawukhishwa imitsefosimiso letawucinisekisa kutsi loku akutsintsi kabi tisebenti letingatfoli selekelelo nalesetikhulile.
tsn: go tla fetisiwa melawana e e tla netefatsang gore seno ga se ame badiri ba ba sa etleediweng gongwe badiri ba bagolwane bosula.

ssw: letinye tinyatselo ticuketfwe kusivumelwano selusha savelonkhe lesasayinwa esoweto ngamabasa lowendlulile.
tsn: dikgato tse dingwe di mo teng ga tumelano ya bosetšhaba ya bašwa e e saenilweng kwa soweto ngogola ka kgwedi ya moranang.

ssw: luhlelo lwetemisebenti lekhulisiwe yahulumende kanye neluhlelo lwemisebenti yahulumende kuyachubeka nekuba siphephelo lesinemandla salabaphuyile kanye nelusha.
tsn: lenaane le le atolositsweng la ditiro tsa setšhaba le lenaane la tiro ya baagi a tswelela go nna tshegetso e e bokgoni ya batlhoki le bašwa.

ssw: sakhe ematfuba emisebenti letigidzi leti-3.7 kuleminyaka lesihlanu leyengcile.
tsn: re tlhamile ditšhono tsa ditiro di le dimilione di le 3,7 mo dingwageng di le tlhano tse di fetileng.

ssw: bantfu betfu batfola imali lengenako nemakhono eluhlelweni lwetemisebenti yahulumende, labawasebentisela kutfola kucashwa lokuhlelekile.
tsn: batho ba rona ba amogela lotseno le bokgoni go tswa mo lenaaneng la ditiro tsa setšhaba, mme ba dirise tseo go batla tiro e e siameng.

ssw: ikhabhinethi itibekele umgomo wekusungula ematfuba emisebenti letigidzi letisitfupha kusukela kulomnyaka kuye ku-2019, kucondvwe lusha.
tsn: kabinete e ipeetse seelo sa ditšhono tsa ditiro di le dimilione di le 6 go tloga monongwaga go ya go 2019, go lebeletswe bašwa.

ssw: luhlelo lwetfu lwekusita kutenhlalo manje lolufinyelela kubantfu labatigidzi leti-16, luniketa tekuphepha kubantfu labatigidzi, ikakhulu bantfwana labasengotini.
tsn: lenaneo la rona la thuso ya loago le ga jaanong le fitlhelelang batho ba ka nna dimilione di le 16, le tlametsa dimilione ka pabalesego, bogolo thata bana ba ba mo matshosetsing.

ssw: imiti leminyenti itfola kusitakala ngenca yetibonelelo tahulumende, imali yebantfwana, impesheni yalabadzala neyalabakhubatekile.
tsn: malapa a le mantsi a ungwelwa go tswa mo dithusong tsa puso tse e leng thuso ya tlamelo ya bana, phenšene gammogo le thuso ya bogole.

ssw: letibonelelo titawuchubeka njalo ngoba imiti leminyenti itfola kusitakala ngobe ematfuba emisebenti ayimvelalakancane ngalesikhatsi semnotfo lobutsakatsaka.
tsn: puso e tla tswelela go duela dithuso tseno gonne bontsi jwa magae bo ikaegile ka tsona ka ntlha ya fa ditšhono tsa tiro di se kalo mo nakong eno e e thata ya kwelotlase ya ikonomi.

ssw: lamatfuba latfolakala kuhulumende, enta kutsi sisho ngekutigcabha sitsi, iningizimu afrika lesiphila kuyo lamuhla, incono kakhulu kunaleyo besiphila kuyo ngembi kwa-1994.
tsn: ditšhono tseno tse di dirwang ke puso, di re kgontsha gore re bue ka boipelo gore ga jaana re nna mo nageng e e botoka thata fa e bapisiwa le e re neng re nna mo go yona pele ga 1994. bakaulengwe.

ssw: bantfu bakitsi,sisesikhatsini lesimatima.
tsn: re sa ntse re le mo pakeng e e boima.

ssw: tintfo letenteka emnotfweni wasemelika setiholele ekuweni kwetimakethe tetimali lebetisavela, kufaka ekhatsi lirandi.
tsn: ditiragalo tsa ikonomi ya amerika di bakile kwelotlase e e bonako mo mading a mebaraka e e sa ntseng e tlhagelela, go akarediwa le ranta.

ssw: nga-2013, lirandi lehle nga-17,6 wemaphesenthi nalicatsaniswa nelidola lasemelika.
tsn: mo tsamaong ya 2013, ranta e wetse tlase ka 17.6% kgatlhanong le dolara ya amerika.

ssw: silinangisonani sekuntjintjiselana siveta ingoti lenkhulu yekwehla nekwenyuka kwentsengo.
tsn: seelo se se bokoa sa thefosanyo se matshosetsi a a boitshegang mo infoleišeneng mme gape se tla dira gore lenaane la rona la mafaratlhatlha le nne tlhotlhwagodimo.

ssw: nanoma kunjalo, tinkampani letitfumela imphahla ngaphandle kulamanye emave, ikakhulu umkhakha lokhicitako, kufanele tisebentise lelitfuba lekwehla kwemandla elirandi kanye nekuvuka lokunemandla emaveni emhlaba.
tsn: le gale, ditlamo tse di romelang ntle, bogolo segolo mo maphateng a tlhagiso, di tshwanetse go dirisa ranta e e bokoa le itharabologelo e kgolo ya lefatshe lotlhe.

ssw: njengoba sisenaletinselele, siyati kutsi singamelana nalesikhatsi sebumatima.
tsn: le fa re na le mathata ano, re a itse gore re ka kgona mo pakeng eno ya dintelo.

ssw: sente njalo phambilini kuleminyaka lesihlanu leyengcile.
tsn: re setse re kile ra dira jalo mo dingwageng tse tlhano tse di fetileng.

ssw: sitawuvuka, ecinisweni, sitawuvuka sinemandla kunaphambilini nasingenta tintfo letifanele.
tsn: tota, re tla tlhagelela re maatlafetse le go feta fa re ka dira dilo tse di siameng.

ssw: sifanele sisebentisane singuhulumende, temabhizinisi netisebenti kute sikhulise umnotfo wetfu ngesilinganiso lesingetulu kwemaphesenti lasihlanu kute kutsi sikhone kwakha imisebenti lesiyidzingako.
tsn: re tshwanetse go dira mmogo jaaka puso, kgwebo le badiri go godisa ikomomi ka seelo se se kwa godimo ga 5% gore re kgone go tlhama ditiro tse re di tlhokang.

ssw: ngenhlanhla lenhle lokusebentisana sekuvele kuyenteka.
tsn: ka lesego, tirisanommogo eno e setse e ntse e tsweletse.

ssw: kwenteka ku-nedlac lekungulesinye setikhungo letibalulekile tekusebentisana kuntsandvo yetfu yelinyenti, emkhatsini wahulumende, temabhizinisi, tisebenti kanye nemkhakha wemmango.
tsn: e diragala kwa lekgotla la bosetšhaba la tlhabololo ya ikonomi le ya ditiro, e leng sengwe sa ditheo tsa botlhokwa tsa tirisanommogo mo temokerasing ya rona, magareng ga puso, kgwebo, badiri le baagi.

ssw: kwenteke ngisho nasekukhulumisaneni lebesiba nako nemmango wetemabhizinisi.
tsn: e diragetse gape mo dipuisanong tse re nnileng natso le bagwebi.

ssw: kulomnyaka lophelile ngicale kubandzakanya temabhizinisi etinyatselweni letitsite hulumende langatitsatsa kute kube lula kuchuba emabhizinisi kulelive lakitsi.
tsn: mo ngwageng yo o fetileng ke ne ka simolola go buisana le bagwebi ka ga dikgato tse di rileng tse puso e ka di tsayang go nolofatsa go dira kgwebo mo nageng ya rona.

ssw: lokwavela kuleyo nchubo kutsi manje, sesente kuvunywa kwekulawula nekuniketa emalayisensi ekuhlola lifutse letesimondzawo, emalayisensi emanti newasemayini kusebente kahle kakhulu nangemphumelelo.
tsn: go tswa mo thulaganyong eo, jaanong re rulagantse dithebolo tsa taolo le dilaesense tsa tshekatsheko ya kamego ya tikologo, dilaesense tsa metsi mmogo le dilaesense tsa meepo.

ssw: iphalamende isaphotfula tichibiyelo temtsetfo lotawunika emandla lentfuntfuko lenhle, kutawenteka ngaphansi kwemalanga lange-300, sikhatsi lesitsatfwako nakucalwa imayini, kusukela nakufakwa sicelo kudzimate kube sekuvunyweni kwekugcina.
tsn: palamente e konosetsa dipaakanyo tsa bofelelo tsa molao gore ntlha eno e e siameng e dirisiwe, mme seo se tla fokotsa nako ya go simolola moepo go ya go malatsi a a ka fa tlase ga 300, go tloga ka go dira kopo go fitlha kwa go rebolweng.

ssw: lisekela lamengameli weriphabhulikhi liyachubeka nekuchuba tingcoco emkhatsini wahulumende, tinkampani tetimayini kanye netisebenti.
tsn: motlatsamoporesidente wa rephaboliki o tswelela go gokaganya dipuisano magareng ga puso, ditlamo tsa meepo le badiri.

ssw: inhloso yaloku kusimamisa tebudlelwane kutetimboni kulomkhakha lobalulekile wetemnotfo wetfu.
tsn: maikemisetso ke go tsepamisa dikamano le badiri mo lephateng leno la botlhokwa la ikonomi ya rona.

ssw: lenchubo ikhipha imiphumela.
tsn: seno se ungwa maungo.

ssw: titeleka kulomnyaka lophelile kulomkhakha tibe mbalwa futsi taba tesikhatsi lesincane.
tsn: dikhuduego mo lephateng leno di nnile mmalwa fela mme e bile ga di a tsaya sebaka.

ssw: futsi lokubaluleke kakhulu kutsi, tinchubo tetetimboni tenteka ngekuhambisana nemtsetfo ngalokungagucuki.
tsn: mme sa botlhokwa, dithulaganyo tsa dikamano tsa badiri di diragala ka tsela e e mo molaong.

ssw: siye sangenelela kutetimayini ngobe ngutona letibaluleke kakhulu ekwakheni ematfuba emisebenti.
tsn: re tseregantse mo meepong gonne e le mothapi yo mogolo.

ssw: sidzinga umkhakha wetimayini losebentako.
tsn: re tlhoka lephata la meepo le le dirang sentle.

ssw: timayini ticasha bantfu labangetulu kwahhafu wesigidzi.
tsn: meepo e thapa batho ba feta halofo ya milione.

ssw: ngutona letingumkhakha lomkhulu wemali lengenako levela emaveni angaphandle kulelive letfu.
tsn: ke moamogedi yo mogolo wa madi a dinaga tse di kwa ntle mo nageng ya rona.

ssw: tibuye futsi tifake tigidzigidzi letinge-20 temarandi letingena ngco kumalingena yentsela.
tsn: gape e tsenya madi a ka nna r20 bilione ka tlhamalalo mo lotsenong lwa lekgetho.

ssw: tetimayini tibuye futsi kube ngito letifaka sandla kakhulu njengemtsengi wemphahla netinsita, kanye nemfakigalelo kuleminye imikhakha yemnotfo wetfu naleminye iminotfo emhlabeni jikelele.
tsn: gape meepo e na le seabe se segolo jaaka moreki wa dithoto le ditirelo, mmogo le motlamedi wa ditshwaelo mo maphateng a mangwe a ikonomi ya rona mmogo le di-ikonomi tse dingwe lefatshe ka bophara.

ssw: sihlola kubambisana nalabatsintsekako kute kubukwe ludzaba lwetindlu tekuhlala emadolobheni lanetimayini.
tsn: re sekaseka tirisanommogo le baamegi go samagana le ntlha ya dintlo kwa ditoropong tse di nang le meepo.

ssw: akengiphindze futsi ngikhumbute tinkampani tetimbiwa kutsi 2014 ngumncamulajucu wato wekutfutfukisa tetindlu netimo tekuhlala tebavukuti kanye nekuzuza lokunyeti lokuhlosiwe.
tsn: nte ke gakolole ditlamo tsa meepo gape gore 2014 ke letlha la bofelo la gore di tokafatse dintlo le seemo sa botshelo sa badiri ba meepo mmogo le go fitlhelela diphitlhelelo tsa bontsi jo bo rileng.

ssw: hulumende uyachubeka nekulandzelela nekuphocelela kuhambisana kuko kokubili tinhlelo tetenhlalo netetisebenti tetimayini kanye nalokuhloswe yishatha yetimayini.
tsn: puso e tswelela go ela tlhoko le go netefatsa kobamelo ya diphitlhelelo tsa maano a ditlamo a loago le badiri mmogo le tšhata ya meepo.

ssw: bantfu bakitsi baseningizimu afrika,malunga lahloniphekile,ngaphandle kwetetimayini, sibuye satfola lokunye lokusihlanu lobekukhicita imisebenti nga-2009.
tsn: maaforika borwa ka nna,ditokololo tse di tlotlegang,kwa ntle ga meepo, re supile maphata a mangwe a matlhano a a ka susumetsang ditiro ka 2009. ona ke bojanala, temothuo, ikonomi e e tala, tlhabololo ya mafaratlhatlha le tlhagiso.

ssw: loku bekutekuvakasha, tekulima, temnotfo letinganukubeti simondzawo nemvelo, kutfutfukiswa kwetakhiwonchanti netekukhicita.
tsn: indaseteri ya bojanala e godile ka tsela e e gakgamatsang.

ssw: nga-1993 iningizimu afrika yatfola tivakashi tangaphandle letitigidzi letintsatfu.
tsn: ka 1993, aforika borwa e amogetse baeng ba ba tswang kwa ntle ba le dimilione di le tharonyana fela.

ssw: nga-2012 lelinani lakhula laba tivakashi letitigidzi leti-13.
tsn: ka 2012, palo eo e ne e godile go fitlha go baeng ba le dimilione di le 13. re tla tswelapele go godisa indaseteri eno, go lebeletswe bokgoni jwa yona jwa go tlhama ditiro.

ssw: sitawuchubeka nekukhulisa lemboni, ngenca yekukhona kwakha imisebenti.
tsn: ka 2012 re ribolotse leano la bosetšhaba la mafaratlhatlha, le le eteletsweng pele ke moporesidente ka khomišene ya moporesidente ya bogokaganyo jwa mafaratlhatlha.

ssw: ekuhambeni kwesikhatsi sikhone kutjala sigidzigidzi sinye lesiphindvwe katsatfu kutakhiwonchanti temmango kuleminyaka lesihlanu leyengcile.
tsn: morago ga moo re ne ra beeletsa r1 tirilione mo mafaratlhatlheng a setšhaba mo tsamaong ya dingwageng di le tlhano tse di fetileng.

ssw: leminyenti yalemiklamo seyiphotfuliwe noma seyidvute kuphotfulwa.
tsn: bontsi jwa diporojeke bo setse bo konoseditswe kgotsa bo gaufi le go konosediwa.

ssw: ngitawubala nje lembalwa.
tsn: ke tla nopola di se kae fela.

ssw: luhlelo lwemabhasi latfutsa aphindzelela i-rea vaya ejozi manje lusetjentiswa bahlali basegauteng labangetulu kwaba-100 000. tinhlelo letifana nalolu tiyakhiwa ekapa, etshwane, enelson mandela bay, ebuffalo city, ethekwini naserustenburg.
tsn: tsamaiso ya rea vaya kwa johannesburg ga jaana e dirisiwa ke baagi ba gauteng ba feta 100 000. ditsamaiso tse di tshwanang le tseo di agiwa kwa motsekapa, tshwane, nelson mandela bay, buffalo city, ethekwini le rustenburg.

ssw: lugu lolusikhumulo semikhumbi selwentiwe lwaba ncono.
tsn: maemelakepe a naga a tokafaditswe.

ssw: sesakhe liphayiphi lekuhambisa emafutsa lelingemakhilomitha lasikhombisa lelisuka ethekwini liya egauteng kute litfutse tigidzigidzi letine temakhiyubhikhi emalitha aphethiloli, dizili naphethiloli wetindizamshini ngemnyaka.
tsn: re agile mola wa peipi ya lookwane wa dikilomitara di le 700 o o tswang kwa durban go leba gauteng go tsamaisa dibilione di le 4 tsa dikhubiki tsa dilitara tsa peterolo, disele le lookwane la difofane ka ngwaga.

ssw: sekwakhiwe imigwaco lemisha noma imizila lecishe ifike kumakhilomitha layi-1500.
tsn: go agilwe dikilomitara di ka nna 1 500 tsa ditsela tse dintšhwa.

ssw: lenchubekelembili mayelana nemigwaco isikhumbuta labo labasebentele lohulumende phambilini labebafunela lelive lokuphuma embili, njengendvuna yetetitfutsi yaphambilini, umnu.
tsn: tswelelopele eno e e amanang le ditsela e re gakolola ka bangwe ba ba dirileng mo pusong eno ba ba neng ba eleletsa naga ya rona tse di gaisang, go tshwana le tona ya maloba ya dipalangwa rre dullar omar.

ssw: kwakhiwa kwemizila lemisha yesitimela sekucalile empumalanga, kute kunciphise kugcwala kwetitfutsi emigwacweni.
tsn: go simolotswe ka kago ya mela e mentšhwa ya seporo kwa mpumalanga, go fokotsa kgatelelo mo ditseleng.

ssw: umklamo wegautrain manje usebenta ngalokuphelele futsi itfwala bagibeli labangetulu kwetigidzi leti-1,2 ngenyanga.
tsn: porojeke ya gautrain jaanong e dira ka botlalo mme e rora bapalami ba feta 1,2 milione ka kgwedi.

ssw: sikhungo sekutfwala bagibeli ngaloliwe saseningizimu afrika sitawusebentisa ngetulu kwetigidzigidzi leti-120 temarandi kuleminyaka lelishumi letako kutsenga titimela letinsha.
tsn: setlamo sa setheo sa diporo le banamedi sa aforika borwase tla dirisa madi a a fetang r120 bilione mo tsamaong ya dingwageng tse di latelang di le 10, go reka diterena tse dintšhwa.

ssw: i-transnet yetfula indlelalisu yayo lenkhulu yaloko lokudzingwa yimakethe lebita tigidzidzi temarandi letinge-300, yekwakha sakhiwonchanti setitfutsi lesidzingeka kakhulu.
tsn: transnet e diragatsa togamaano ya yona e e boitshegang e e lebeletseng tlhokego mo mmarakeng, ya r300 bilione, go aga mafaratlhatlha a a tlhokegang go gaisa a dipalangwa.

ssw: kute sitfole emandla etemnotfo lokhona enshonalanga kapa naselugwini lwasenshonalanga, setfule indzawo yekutfutfukisa timboni esaldanha sabuye futsi savula timboni letimbili letinsha e-atlantis.
tsn: go fitlhelela bokgoni jwa ikonomi jwa kapabophirima le lebopo la bophirima, re tlhomile lefelo la tlhabololo ya diindasteri tsa saldanha mme re butse difeme tse dintšhwa di le pedi kwa atlantis.

ssw: kute kwentiwe ncono kuphakelwa kwemanti, kuphotfulwe kwakhiwa kwemadamu lamakhulu lamabili, i-de hoop elimpopo kanye ne-spring grove kwazulu-natal, bese kutsi umlente wesibili wemklamo i-lesotho highlands water wetfulwe madvute nje.
tsn: go tokafatsa tlamelo ya metsi, go konoseditswe matamo a magolo a mantšhwa a le mabedi, de hoop kwa limpopo mmogo le spring grove kwa kwazulu-natal, fa legato la 2 la porojeke ya metsi ya lesotho highlands e tla tlhongwa mo bogautshwaneng.

ssw: kwakha kuyachubeka esiteshini lesisha sekuphehla gezi, i-medupi elimpopo, i-kusile empumalanga ne-ingula dvutane naseladysmith, kucashwe tisebenti letingetulu kwe-300 000. siyachubeka nekufuna leminye imitfombo yemandla, ngekuhambisana neluhlelo loluhlanganisile lwemtfombo wemandlakutfutfukiswa kwemafutsa i-petroleum, ikakhulu gesi wetinhlese (shale) kutawuba nguyonantfo legucula indlela besisolomane senta ngayo tintfo esigodzini sasekaroo kanye nakumnotfo waseningizimu afrika .
tsn: go tsweletswe ka kago ya diteišene tse dintšhwa tsa maatla, medupi kwa limpopo, kusile kwa mpumalanga le ingula gaufi le ladysmith, mme tsona di thapa badiri ba feta 30 000. re tswelela go sekaseka metswedi e mengwe ya maatla, go lepalepana le leano le le kopanetsweng la ditlamelo tsa maatla.

ssw: ngemuva kwekuhlola tingoti nematfuba, umtsetfosimiso wekugcina utawetfulwa madvute nje futsi utawulandzelwa ekucutjungulweni nasekukhishweni kwemalayisensi.
tsn: go tlhagisiwa ga peteroliamo, bogolo segolo gase ya šale, go tla fetola selebo sa kgaolo ya karoo mmogo le ikonomi ya aforika borwa.

ssw: silindzele kuphetsa kutfolwa kwemamegawatsi latinkhulungwane letiyimfica nemakhulu lasitfupha emandla enuzi.
tsn: morago ga go sekaseka matshosetsi le ditšhono, go tla gololwa melawana ya bofelo fa gautshwane mme yona e tla latelwa ke tsamaiso le thebolo ya dilaesense.

ssw: emafutsa lakhiwa ngetitjalo akhetsiwe futsi asacalile kusebenta.
tsn: re solofetse go konosetsa theko ya dimekawate di le 9 600 tsa maatla a nyutlilia.

ssw: malunga lahloniphekilekwetfu nje, live lelisebenta mbamba futsi seliyindzawo lencono kakhulu yekuhlala.
tsn: ditokololo tse di tlotlegangruri naga ya rona ke naga e e dirang mme ke lefelo le go leng botoka go nna mo go lona.

ssw: sifanele kutsi singaphelelwa ngulomfutfo.
tsn: re tshwanetse go tsweletsa seo.

ssw: malunga lahloniphekile,umnotfo wetfu lomunye lomnyenti wakheka ku-inthanethi noma ngetekuchumanisana.
tsn: ditokololo tse di tlotlegang,bontsi jwa lehumo la rona le dirwa mo inthaneteng gongwe ka tlhaeletsano ya megala.

ssw: intsambo yagezi lenemicu leminyenti lebudze lobungemakhilomitha lange-37 000 ifakwe ngumkhakha wangasese kanye newesive kuleminyaka lesihlanu leyengcile.
tsn: go adilwe mogala wa faeba opotiki wa dikilomitara di le 37 000 ke maphata a poraefete le a setšhaba mo dingwageng di le tlhano tse di fetileng.

ssw: loku kutawukhuliswa kakhulu kuleminyaka letako.
tsn: seno se tla atolosiwa thata mo dingwageng tse di latelang.

ssw: siyatigcabha ngemiphumela yetfu kutesayensi nebucwepheshe.
tsn: re motlotlo ka katlego ya rona mo go tsa saense le thekenoloji.

ssw: kwakhiwa kwesikhulisikubona sekucala (telescope) lesinetindishi letinge-64 ku-sizindza sekucwaninga ngalokwenteka emhlabeni, i-meerkat, kutawuphotfulwa ngekota yekucala ya-2014.
tsn: go tla konosediwa kago ya thelesekoupu ya ntlha ya dijana di le 64 fa go lebilwe kwa arei ya sekwere kilometara, e leng meerkat, mo kotareng ya ntlha ya 2014. ditokololo tse di tlotlegang,diketleetso tsa rona tsa go susumetsa tlhagiso di nnile le dipoelo.

ssw: malunga lahloniphekile,sinikamdlandla setfu sekukhuphula tekukhicita sesivete imiphumela lemihle.
tsn: sekema sa peeletso ya dijanaga se se tlhomilweng ka 2009 se reboletse diketleetso tsa boleng jwa r3.8 bilione go beelediwa mo diporojekeng tsa peeletso di ka nna 160. tsona di tshegetsa ditiro di feta dikete di le 50. ditlamo di tla bo di dira dikoloi, dithekisi mmogo le dibese.

ssw: luhlelo lwelutjalomali lwetimoto lolwetfulwa nga-2009 seluvume tinikamandla letilingana samba lesitigidzigidzi leti-3,8 temarandi temiklamo yelutjalomali lengaba li-160.
tsn: re tsepamisitse lephata la diaparo, dikhai, letlalo le ditlhako, le le neng le kgaola ditiro.

ssw: letinkampani titawube tikhicita timoto letingema-sedan, emakhumbi nemabhasi.
tsn: tsona di akaretsa dibese, merogo e e mo metemeng, diaparo, dikhai, letlalo, ditlhako mmogo le dithoto tse dingwe.

ssw: sisungule umkhakha wetimphahla, tindvwangu, tikhumba kanye neticatfulo, lebewusolomane unciphisa imisebenti.
tsn: mo dingwageng di le pedi tse di fetileng fela, go agilwe dithekisi di feta 20 000 le dibese di le 330 mo gae, mme seno se ngoketse dipeeletso le tlhabololo mo ditoropong tsa rona.

ssw: timboni letimbalwa tentelwe kukhicita imikhicito yakuleli.
tsn: mo dingwageng di le tlhano tse di latelang, mmuso o tla reka bonnye 75% ya dithoto le ditirelo go tswa mo batlhagising ba aforika borwa.

ssw: loku kufaka ekhatsi emabhasi, tibhidvo letifakwe etikoteleni, tembatfo, tindvwangu, tikhumba neticatfulo kanye naleminye imikhicito.
tsn: maaforika borwa ka nna,re tshwanetse go dira ka natla go tlhabolola batlhagisi ba ba tlhagelelang gongwe ba bantsho.

ssw: sinetibonelo temphumelelo letibonakalako teluhlelo lwekwenta imikhicito kuleli lakitsi.
tsn: bontsi jwa batlhagisi ba ba simololang ba bantsho ba ngongorega ka mathata a ba a itemogelang go bona matlole a tlhagiso, mebaraka ya batlamedi le bareki, mmogo le tshegetso ya setegeniki ya tlhagiso.

ssw: kuleminyaka lemibili leyendlulile kuphela, emakhumbi langematekisi langetulu kwala-200 000 nemabhasi lange-330 akhicitwa kuleli lakitsi, lokwaletsa lutjalomali nentfutfuko emadolobheni lamkhulu akitsi.
tsn: letlole la bosetšhaba la maatlafatso, koporasi ya tlhabololo ya indaseteri le setheo sa matlole sa dikgwebopotlana, di tla tswelela go tlamela dikgwebo tse di kgonegang tsa bantsho ka matlole go tsweletsa diindasteri.

ssw: bantfu bakitsi baseningizimu afrika,sifanele sisebente ngekutikhandla lokukhulu kute sitfutfukise bosotimboni labasafufusa noma labamnyama.
tsn: go tlaleletsa foo, re rotloetsa dikgwebo tse di godileng go tshegetsa tlhabololo ya dikgwebo tsa tlhagiso tsa bantsho.

ssw: linyenti labosotimboni labasafufusa likhonona ngebumatima lelihlangabetana nabo ekutfoleni timali tekwesekela timboni tabo, lababatsengisela imikhicito kanye netimakethe labangatsengisa kuto, kanye nekusitwa ngemikhicito ngekwethekhinikhi.
tsn: temothuo ke mothapi yo mogolo le motlamedi wa ditšhono tsa bogwebi.

ssw: sikhwama savelonkhe sekuhlomisa, nenhlangano yekutfutfukisa timboni kanye ne-ejensi lesita emabhizinisi lamancane ngetimali kutawuchubeka kunikete timali emabhizinisi lasebentako ebantfu labamnyama kute kukhutsatwe timboni.
tsn: lenaane la rona la tshegetso ya temothuo, fetsa tlala, le tlhagisa baromelantle ba bantšhwa.

ssw: tekulima tiphuma embili ekuveteni ematfuba emisebenti nekuniketa ematfuba ekuba bosomabhizinisi.
tsn: re tla tsweletsa le lephata la rona la botshwaratlhapi, le le tsenyang madi a a fopholediwang go r6 bilione mo ikonoming mme le tlamela ka ditiro di le 27 000. ditokololo tse di tlotlegang,re nnile le tswelelopele e e bonalang mo lenaaneng la ntšhwafatso ya naga.
